          "scid": "sn56.81:1.2",
          "pli": "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye naccagītavāditavisūkadassanā paṭiviratā; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye naccagītavāditavisūkadassanā appaṭiviratā. Taṃ kissa hetu … pe …. ",
          "en": "“… the sentient beings who refrain from dancing, singing, music, and seeing shows are few, while those who don’t refrain are many …” "
